import math

def count_valid_pairs(test_cases):
    results = []
    for case in test_cases:
        (N, A) = case
        count_2 = A.count(2)
        count_0 = A.count(0)
        valid_pairs = math.comb(count_2, 2) - math.comb(count_0, 2)
        results.append(valid_pairs)
    return results
